::Rex/Firearm::

Rex looks over at Brix, shaking his head. "They're chasing several Maximals. 
It looks like there's one dead there."

Rex turns his head as Firearm looks at him. "Its too thick to get through."

Rex nods, "You know what that means."

"Yup. Tank mode!" Firearm transforms into a big tank, falling down toward the 
rainforest. Threes bend and snap as he reaches the canopy, falling at 
Imprisoner.
